### Create a module (admin only)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/modules
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "title": "Wildlife Identification Basics",
  "description": "Learn to identify common Bornean wildlife species"
}

###

### List modules
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/modules
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### Get a module
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/modules/{{moduleId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### Update a module
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/modules/{{moduleId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "description": "Updated description for wildlife identification"
}

###

### Publish a module (notifies all active guides)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/modules/{{moduleId}}/publish
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### Archive a module
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/modules/{{moduleId}}/archive
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### Delete a module (blocked if enrolments or certifications exist)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/modules/{{moduleId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
